                        <p class="lead">
I build data-intensive systems that are more scalable, more robust, and more predictable.
I draw from advanced statistical models to deliver practical database solutions to real-world problems.
In particular, I adapt concepts and tools from applied statistics, optimization theory, and machine learning.
</p>
